'''Tieress''' was the title held by the spouses of the [[Satab]]s of [[Ventooine/Legends|Ventooine]]. Their duties were unknown, but they were members of the royal family and held power over the royal guard. The only known Tieress is [[Chrysalla]], who held the title sometime prior to [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]]. She betrayed her [[Satab (individual)|husband]] and helped end the Satab rule on Ventooine.

